512
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:11,680
Por quê?

513
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:13,000
Bem...

514
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:15,360
Teoricamente,

515
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:19,320
